{"_id":"uIo5zM9QCWbAkrMD","name":"the Respectable Mr and Mrs Mars - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00j80y6z01hxy4y8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"yEpMRU0bc2vMn39H","name":"the Respectable Mr and Mrs Mars - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00j80y6z01hxy4y8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"We are a harmless middle-aged couple and no one would ever consider \nus a danger. We are adept at going unnoticed. Our passion for human \nfood drives us to real binges.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"We are a harmless middle-aged couple and no one would ever consider us a danger. We are adept at going unnoticed. Our passion for human food drives us to real binges.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ZNh0tphqMAc37MOx","name":"the Respectable Mr and Mrs Mars - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00j80y6z01hxy4y8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"We are always connected to the Mars Operations Center, and this \nallows us to have information about history and science. We are \nmorbidly attracted to any form of art because it is totally absent on our \nworld.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"We are always connected to the Mars Operations Center, and this allows us to have information about history and science. We are morbidly attracted to any form of art because it is totally absent on our world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"68hZlhW21yuQvQzv","name":"the Respectable Mr and Mrs Mars - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00j80y6z01hxy4y8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Dark Ego Descriptor","descriptorRole":"dark-ego-descriptor","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Our knowledge is far more advanced than human knowledge, and we \nhave incredible technology at our disposal. We always try to help those \nwho are considered outcasts or excluded from society...","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"Our knowledge is far more advanced than human knowledge, and we have incredible technology at our disposal. We always try to help those who are considered outcasts or excluded from society...","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"e9fKBOsBdDAgYi7w","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"017xel74001lh0wn","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Porziella, my faithful flea, is always with me and has guarded my \nback like a trusted servant. Over time, I have trained Porziella to \nperform various tasks, including very complex ones. Porziella loves \nhuman blood, and although this disgusts people, I try to satisfy her \nwhenever I can.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Porziella, my faithful flea, is always with me and has guarded my back like a trusted servant. Over time, I have trained Porziella to perform various tasks, including very complex ones. Porziella loves human blood, and although this disgusts people, I try to satisfy her whenever I can.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"8QmKPaTQvIzuayMY","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"017xel74001lh0wn","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I learned some magic tricks from seven bandits, all of them brothers, \nand I know about arcane arts. I am attracted to magic and want to \ngather all knowledge about it.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I learned some magic tricks from seven bandits, all of them brothers, and I know about arcane arts. I am attracted to magic and want to gather all knowledge about it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"v3RLn2DD0Zw72zvU","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6 - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"017xel74001lh0wn","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am courageous and stubborn. When I speak about justice and \nequality, the passion that animates me touches people’s hearts. For me, \nthe cause comes before everything and I am ready to take any action, \neven the most extreme.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am courageous and stubborn. When I speak about justice and equality, the passion that animates me touches people’s hearts. For me, the cause comes before everything and I am ready to take any action, even the most extreme.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 6","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"eljCXUoiZFoiBsKc","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01c38mlp00wvjrve","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have extremely keen eyesight and no detail escapes me. I can see \neverything, even in the dark or in the thickest fog. Sometimes I don’t \nunderstand whether the things I see are real or just a figment of my \nimagination.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have extremely keen eyesight and no detail escapes me. I can see everything, even in the dark or in the thickest fog. Sometimes I don’t understand whether the things I see are real or just a figment of my imagination.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"R3FmES4ApvkGoYry","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01c38mlp00wvjrve","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am used to walking around completely naked, so my physique is \ntough. I hate having unnecessary things on me, except for my beloved \ncrown.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am used to walking around completely naked, so my physique is tough. I hate having unnecessary things on me, except for my beloved crown.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Y167iSr58Rtrr4UR","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9 - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01c38mlp00wvjrve","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am good with words, I know etiquette, and I know how to dazzle the \ncrowd. I cannot refrain from commenting with the utmost sincerity \non the way my interlocutors dress.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am good with words, I know etiquette, and I know how to dazzle the crowd. I cannot refrain from commenting with the utmost sincerity on the way my interlocutors dress.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 9","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"7nEOJuhFrYoCpOqo","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"0187e6w300c0txw8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can \nspend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects:\n1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast \nand allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible \nobstacle.\n2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or \ndetails of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift.\n3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action \nthat is not intended to harm anyone. \n4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can spend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects: 1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast and allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible obstacle. 2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or details of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift. 3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action that is not intended to harm anyone. 4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"QJyeNN8IXckpvKzd","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"0187e6w300c0txw8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I have an unusual mind and remember every detail, even years \nlater. My body is puny and I hate to do strenuous work.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I have an unusual mind and remember every detail, even years later. My body is puny and I hate to do strenuous work.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"fGBTjDyRw5nCK0Lh","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"0187e6w300c0txw8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I have charisma to spare and I am a smooth talker who commands \nrespect and admiration. I must always have the last word.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I have charisma to spare and I am a smooth talker who commands respect and admiration. I must always have the last word.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"nT5e8msZexkZtr7E","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7 - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"0187e6w300c0txw8","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Dark Ego Descriptor","descriptorRole":"dark-ego-descriptor","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"It only takes me a few seconds to assess the situation and use it to \nmy advantage. I have a soft spot for loving families who remind me \nof what I will never have.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"It only takes me a few seconds to assess the situation and use it to my advantage. I have a soft spot for loving families who remind me of what I will never have.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 7","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"umPH1whSPprXc0Qk","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01bt90wq00mg6uvt","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled Hunter and know what it takes to survive in wild \nplaces. I find it hard to trust anyone, but when I do, I never question \nthe good faith of the person I have chosen.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am a skilled Hunter and know what it takes to survive in wild places. I find it hard to trust anyone, but when I do, I never question the good faith of the person I have chosen.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"asTzwawxk26wqRYD","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01bt90wq00mg6uvt","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"My senses are keen and my body is hardened by the outdoors. I hate \nbig cities, hustle and bustle, and generally can’t stand people who talk \ntoo much.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"My senses are keen and my body is hardened by the outdoors. I hate big cities, hustle and bustle, and generally can’t stand people who talk too much.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"2GRF4ZvCOgULSxSB","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8 - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01bt90wq00mg6uvt","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am trained to kill all kinds of beasts and know how to use the \nhunting grounds to my advantage. Monsters must always be \ndestroyed, for them I see no mercy or redemption.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am trained to kill all kinds of beasts and know how to use the hunting grounds to my advantage. Monsters must always be destroyed, for them I see no mercy or redemption.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 8","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"dY80l1s95VQAIAcj","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00dimi9x00ieq7m6","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for each Check you make when trying \nto persuade someone to do the right thing. Once per Scenario, if you \nsuffer 1 Wound to stand up for what you believe in, you set an example \nfor those who help you. Each ally recovers 1 Soma, and a target of your \nchoice (Hunter or NPC) immediately gains an additional action they \nmust use to try to help you or get you to safety.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for each Check you make when trying to persuade someone to do the right thing. Once per Scenario, if you suffer 1 Wound to stand up for what you believe in, you set an example for those who help you. Each ally recovers 1 Soma, and a target of your choice (Hunter or NPC) immediately gains an additional action they must use to try to help you or get you to safety.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"UB2KBfUOVydJBszp","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00dimi9x00ieq7m6","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am a young prince, well-versed in the etiquette of the court. I \nam a diligent student, my favorite subjects being history and \npoetry. I am not ashamed of my strange appearance and I hate to \nhide from others.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a young prince, well-versed in the etiquette of the court. I am a diligent student, my favorite subjects being history and poetry. I am not ashamed of my strange appearance and I hate to hide from others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"lqCGS9eVYqExX3rP","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00dimi9x00ieq7m6","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I use these qualities to uphold the good name of my family. I will \nnot allow anyone to violate the ideals of justice and courage with \nwhich I was raised.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I use these qualities to uphold the good name of my family. I will not allow anyone to violate the ideals of justice and courage with which I was raised.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vERhvFJOJPMZElHR","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00dimi9x00ieq7m6","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Dark Ego Descriptor","descriptorRole":"dark-ego-descriptor","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have strange powers, and my body is stronger and more resilient \nthan an ordinary child’s. While I’m not ashamed of my \nappearance, these uncanny abilities mark me as different, and I \ntry not to attract attention when I use my power.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I have strange powers, and my body is stronger and more resilient than an ordinary child’s. While I’m not ashamed of my appearance, these uncanny abilities mark me as different, and I try not to attract attention when I use my power.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"M6MEkz88ywnFnDQt","name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01kfc4p4009zcz91","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk","ownerKey":"cazador.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can mentally communicate for the rest of the Scene.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Y ou can mentally communicate for the rest of the Scene.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Qvk101dWECvOFZZj","name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01kfc4p4009zcz91","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk","ownerKey":"cazador.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am an exorcist monk. My body is tempered by a lifetime of asceticism \nand fighting evil spirits. I do not tolerate blasphemy and those who use \nknowledge for personal gain.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I am an exorcist monk. My body is tempered by a lifetime of asceticism and fighting evil spirits. I do not tolerate blasphemy and those who use knowledge for personal gain.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"HadOmgKS9bWo2Agx","name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01kfc4p4009zcz91","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk","ownerKey":"cazador.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"Prayer keeps my mind steadfast and my words are an inspiration to \nthose who have faith. I do not tolerate the concepts of faith and \ndevotion being questioned.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Prayer keeps my mind steadfast and my words are an inspiration to those who have faith. I do not tolerate the concepts of faith and devotion being questioned.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"CXMvdKWUbV7P1csh","name":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01kfc4p4009zcz91","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk","ownerKey":"cazador.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Dark Ego Descriptor","descriptorRole":"dark-ego-descriptor","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"My greatest secret is that I am like those I fight. My true essence is that \nof a Yokai ghost, which is why I have a talent for unearthing Broken \nTales. I try to do good deeds in the hope of reincarnating as a human.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My greatest secret is that I am like those I fight. My true essence is that of a Yokai ghost, which is why I have a talent for unearthing Broken Tales. I try to do good deeds in the hope of reincarnating as a human.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Karasu Kuroi the Wandering Monk","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.karasu-kuroi-the-wandering-monk"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ss96PgHABCPhvrZc","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"018rdea101q785w6","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"If your Champion is knocked out or killed, a new Champion will arrive at \nthe beginning of the next Scenario. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success on all \nChecks where your action removes you from your Champion’s obsessive \nattention.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"If your Champion is knocked out or killed, a new Champion will arrive at the beginning of the next Scenario. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success on all Checks where your action removes you from your Champion’s obsessive attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"JIMkEhd9eT0iulFQ","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"018rdea101q785w6","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I have a talent for assessing people’s merits and flaws, so I am good at \ncoordinating the efforts of those who trust me. I have a soft spot for those \nwho fail but try hard, and though I don’t like to admit it, sometimes the \ninstinct to help losers still takes over.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I have a talent for assessing people’s merits and flaws, so I am good at coordinating the efforts of those who trust me. I have a soft spot for those who fail but try hard, and though I don’t like to admit it, sometimes the instinct to help losers still takes over.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"uxlI1M6d7H4TKpvv","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"018rdea101q785w6","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am very vain and love to waste time admiring my own image.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am very vain and love to waste time admiring my own image.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"56F0zsDutAqw25OW","name":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5 - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"018rdea101q785w6","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5","ownerKey":"cazador.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Dark Ego Descriptor","descriptorRole":"dark-ego-descriptor","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am an ancient fairy and my magic allows me to manipulate and \ndominate water. I don’t like to be recognized by humans, so I try to \nkeep my powers hidden from prying eyes.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am an ancient fairy and my magic allows me to manipulate and dominate water. I don’t like to be recognized by humans, so I try to keep my powers hidden from prying eyes.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Lost Stories Exclusives Hunter 5","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-5"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"kiG0HELYXtcqKY8W","name":"the Pale Medic - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00ke68iz00h1capk","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Pale Medic","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-pale-medic","ownerKey":"cazador.the-pale-medic","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a good doctor and I know the cure for every disease, I can tell the \nphysical state of health of a patient just by looking at them. I hate \nviolence and physical confrontation.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a good doctor and I know the cure for every disease, I can tell the physical state of health of a patient just by looking at them. I hate violence and physical confrontation.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Pale Medic","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-pale-medic"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ZGZTQhukF6dHPii1","name":"the Pale Medic - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00ke68iz00h1capk","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Pale Medic","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-pale-medic","ownerKey":"cazador.the-pale-medic","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I have a certain amount of charm and I know how to put people at ease \nwith my polite manner. I feel uncomfortable in places where I have not \nbeen invited or where it is obvious that my presence is unwelcome.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have a certain amount of charm and I know how to put people at ease with my polite manner. I feel uncomfortable in places where I have not been invited or where it is obvious that my presence is unwelcome.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Pale Medic","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-pale-medic"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"lqYjm1dKE1EkZ4wR","name":"the Pale Medic - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00ke68iz00h1capk","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Pale Medic","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-pale-medic","ownerKey":"cazador.the-pale-medic","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I have vampire blood in me and my strength is far superior to that of \nan ordinary human. I am extremely sensitive to sunlight and try to \navoid it as much as possible.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have vampire blood in me and my strength is far superior to that of an ordinary human. I am extremely sensitive to sunlight and try to avoid it as much as possible.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Pale Medic","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-pale-medic"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"LZqxitn4bxt11yMy","name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"013jbni200ge94bp","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief","ownerKey":"cazador.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am an experienced criminal and I know what it takes to pull off \na perfect heist. Planning and precision are the basis for success, \nand I refuse to rely on improvisation or luck.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am an experienced criminal and I know what it takes to pull off a perfect heist. Planning and precision are the basis for success, and I refuse to rely on improvisation or luck.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Tb9RuAoGM0T6Qmzy","name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"013jbni200ge94bp","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief","ownerKey":"cazador.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"My misdeeds have made me a real celebrity - I have clashed with \nheroes, nobles, and religious people, and I know how to deal with \neach of them. Sometimes I like to give my enemies a small \nadvantage just to make the challenge more interesting.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"My misdeeds have made me a real celebrity - I have clashed with heroes, nobles, and religious people, and I know how to deal with each of them. Sometimes I like to give my enemies a small advantage just to make the challenge more interesting.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"fPdDc27jTKDlSwOE","name":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"013jbni200ge94bp","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief","ownerKey":"cazador.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am as ingenious in the use of concealed weapons and low blows \nas I am in plotting crime. The memory of my lost love has changed \nme deeply, and I try to prevent crime from creating innocent \nvictims.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am as ingenious in the use of concealed weapons and low blows as I am in plotting crime. The memory of my lost love has changed me deeply, and I try to prevent crime from creating innocent victims.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Moriarty the Gentleman Thief","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.moriarty-the-gentleman-thief"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"EVOFtOy8FZjmskN5","name":"the 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00r995py00x1gegb","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-7-hessian-mercenaries","ownerKey":"cazador.the-7-hessian-mercenaries","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Outcome with an Increment: The goal has been reached, and the team has \nbrought home something important. The Storyteller will tell you what.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Outcome with an Increment: The goal has been reached, and the team has brought home something important. The Storyteller will tell you what.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-7-hessian-mercenaries"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vQkgAhk2nLf1f5gN","name":"the 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00r995py00x1gegb","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-7-hessian-mercenaries","ownerKey":"cazador.the-7-hessian-mercenaries","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"We are experienced mercenaries and have seen every battlefield. We \nhate working for free and any chance to bring home some extra loot is \ngood.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are experienced mercenaries and have seen every battlefield. We hate working for free and any chance to bring home some extra loot is good.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-7-hessian-mercenaries"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"K5v6CHq5WZCjuBZq","name":"the 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00r995py00x1gegb","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-7-hessian-mercenaries","ownerKey":"cazador.the-7-hessian-mercenaries","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"We are adept at getting things, information, people, or anything you \nwant - ask and we will find it. We are intolerant of authority and \nanything with a hierarchy of command.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"We are adept at getting things, information, people, or anything you want - ask and we will find it. We are intolerant of authority and anything with a hierarchy of command.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-7-hessian-mercenaries"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"YqkrOGJhDoFwANwY","name":"the 7 Hessian Mercenaries - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00r995py00x1gegb","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-7-hessian-mercenaries","ownerKey":"cazador.the-7-hessian-mercenaries","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Dark Ego Descriptor","descriptorRole":"dark-ego-descriptor","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Discipline and order are the keys to victory. We act as a team because \nthat is what has allowed us to survive so far. Team first and foremost.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Discipline and order are the keys to victory. We act as a team because that is what has allowed us to survive so far. Team first and foremost.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The 7 Hessian Mercenaries","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.the-7-hessian-mercenaries"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"1XWLJUO1whsXm33S","name":"Tremoteus Rumpel - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01s2bpuq009ehhq3","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have an encyclopedic memory and there is no law that I don’t \nknow. I hate to break the rules.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have an encyclopedic memory and there is no law that I don’t know. I hate to break the rules.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"SAumJIKQDwj8zTcX","name":"Tremoteus Rumpel - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01s2bpuq009ehhq3","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"My reputation precedes me, and my word is held in the highest \nregard by anyone with an ounce of honesty. I detest criminals and \nthose who act to harm the innocent. Big or small, a crime is still \na crime.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"My reputation precedes me, and my word is held in the highest regard by anyone with an ounce of honesty. I detest criminals and those who act to harm the innocent. Big or small, a crime is still a crime.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Yabjvt5PSw2HQBdJ","name":"Tremoteus Rumpel - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01s2bpuq009ehhq3","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am a keen disputant and have an uncanny ability to detect \ndeception. I need hard evidence before I’ll accuse someone of \ndishonesty.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a keen disputant and have an uncanny ability to detect deception. I need hard evidence before I’ll accuse someone of dishonesty.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"wMxaiwxmCmzhyFw5","name":"Loki the Deceiver - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01t84tjr01hcujck","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I can disguise myself to assume any identity. I can easily imitate \nmen, women, and even fantastical creatures. I have great respect \nfor a successful deception and hate to expose it, even if it would \nbenefit me.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I can disguise myself to assume any identity. I can easily imitate men, women, and even fantastical creatures. I have great respect for a successful deception and hate to expose it, even if it would benefit me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"gigycI0DDGQ5XTZf","name":"Loki the Deceiver - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01t84tjr01hcujck","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled acrobat, I tell stories, perform magic tricks, and put \nmy audience in a good mood. I enjoy chaos and adding confusion \nto situations is a way for me to bring balance to the world.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a skilled acrobat, I tell stories, perform magic tricks, and put my audience in a good mood. I enjoy chaos and adding confusion to situations is a way for me to bring balance to the world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"x7KIVz4HgyHLxA1X","name":"Loki the Deceiver - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01t84tjr01hcujck","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am a master at distorting and unraveling deception. Verbal \nand body language hold no secrets for me. I don’t like to get my \nhands dirty and would rather have someone else do it for me.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a master at distorting and unraveling deception. Verbal and body language hold no secrets for me. I don’t like to get my hands dirty and would rather have someone else do it for me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"TNuFjoXJ94GuttZa","name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"017zc8s100kc3zn2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.miss-snow-and-lady-storm","ownerKey":"cazador.miss-snow-and-lady-storm","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma when you use this Gift to blow a kiss to the target, \nthus avoiding physical contact.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Y ou can spend 1 Soma when you use this Gift to blow a kiss to the target, thus avoiding physical contact.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.miss-snow-and-lady-storm"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"V0uncA5fuNXKqmaV","name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"017zc8s100kc3zn2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.miss-snow-and-lady-storm","ownerKey":"cazador.miss-snow-and-lady-storm","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am a novice a powerful sorceress with limited power total control \nover cold and snow. My magic can come with dangerous, unintended \nconsequences cause small unwanted effects.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am a novice a powerful sorceress with limited power total control over cold and snow. My magic can come with dangerous, unintended consequences cause small unwanted effects.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.miss-snow-and-lady-storm"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"fDTs5jdC8jBrGwKQ","name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"017zc8s100kc3zn2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.miss-snow-and-lady-storm","ownerKey":"cazador.miss-snow-and-lady-storm","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding dominating people. I have a unique \nability to comprehend their desires. I tend to distrust even close allies \ntrust those I don’t know.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"I am good at understanding dominating people. I have a unique ability to comprehend their desires. I tend to distrust even close allies trust those I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.miss-snow-and-lady-storm"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"NFZ2QilmZqiwekwA","name":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"017zc8s100kc3zn2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.miss-snow-and-lady-storm","ownerKey":"cazador.miss-snow-and-lady-storm","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Dark Ego Descriptor","descriptorRole":"dark-ego-descriptor","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Cold and frost have no effect on me are extensions of my soul and I feel \na great affinity for winter. My heart of pure ice delights is easily touched \nwhen I see others suffer.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cold and frost have no effect on me are extensions of my soul and I feel a great affinity for winter. My heart of pure ice delights is easily touched when I see others suffer.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Miss Snow and Lady Storm","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.miss-snow-and-lady-storm"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"0mVczjIIx7Gi9lhX","name":"the Silent Mother - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"007ezcv300kl1qe2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Silent Mother","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-silent-mother","ownerKey":"cazador.the-silent-mother","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I know my way around high society and have amassed great \nwealth through countless marriages. I am known in the \nunderworld for my exploits. I hate being accused of being a \ncriminal.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I know my way around high society and have amassed great wealth through countless marriages. I am known in the underworld for my exploits. I hate being accused of being a criminal.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Silent Mother","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-silent-mother"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"dezYlUKgf3KcthDj","name":"the Silent Mother - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"007ezcv300kl1qe2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Silent Mother","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-silent-mother","ownerKey":"cazador.the-silent-mother","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am able to understand the potential of young women and know \nhow to guide their steps to develop their true potential. I consider \neach of my protégés a true daughter and would give my life to \nsave them.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am able to understand the potential of young women and know how to guide their steps to develop their true potential. I consider each of my protégés a true daughter and would give my life to save them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Silent Mother","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-silent-mother"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"QPA91FBbyDY4KK5v","name":"the Silent Mother - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"007ezcv300kl1qe2","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Silent Mother","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-silent-mother","ownerKey":"cazador.the-silent-mother","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"Although I appear helpless, I am a capable spy who knows how to \ndefend herself in dangerous situations. I never miss an opportunity \nto accumulate wealth and resources.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Although I appear helpless, I am a capable spy who knows how to defend herself in dangerous situations. I never miss an opportunity to accumulate wealth and resources.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Silent Mother","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-silent-mother"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ofa4HTiD2VgirOQp","name":"Doctor V Frankenstein - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01o5f049013f95ie","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.doctor-v-frankenstein","ownerKey":"cazador.doctor-v-frankenstein","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Gift - Reanimated Corpse: The Creature is immune to electricity and \ncold. Once per Scene, when an ally is about to take 1 Wound, they can \nactivate this Gift to have the Creature intervene in their defense and take \nthe Wound instead. If Victor is the one requesting the use of this Gift, roll \na die: if it comes up even, the Creature will act to save him by applying the \neffect; if it comes up odd, its deep resentment towards its creator will get \nthe better of it and the Creature will not intervene, skipping its possible \nactivation in the Exchange.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"Gift - Reanimated Corpse: The Creature is immune to electricity and cold. Once per Scene, when an ally is about to take 1 Wound, they can activate this Gift to have the Creature intervene in their defense and take the Wound instead. If Victor is the one requesting the use of this Gift, roll a die: if it comes up even, the Creature will act to save him by applying the effect; if it comes up odd, its deep resentment towards its creator will get the better of it and the Creature will not intervene, skipping its possible activation in the Exchange.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.doctor-v-frankenstein"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Y1lBWIDkG06PAJeI","name":"Doctor V Frankenstein - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01o5f049013f95ie","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.doctor-v-frankenstein","ownerKey":"cazador.doctor-v-frankenstein","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am a luminary in physics and medicine and know secrets that the \nbrightest academics can only dream of. I often get lost in my own \nreasoning, which I articulate aloud without realizing it.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a luminary in physics and medicine and know secrets that the brightest academics can only dream of. I often get lost in my own reasoning, which I articulate aloud without realizing it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.doctor-v-frankenstein"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"lmhvKlXSwdyBGwxX","name":"Doctor V Frankenstein - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01o5f049013f95ie","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.doctor-v-frankenstein","ownerKey":"cazador.doctor-v-frankenstein","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I always bring the Creature with me and know how to make the \nmost of its potential. There are times when the guilt of creating such \na monster brings me back to reality, and in those rare moments, I \ntry to do a good deed to atone for my sins.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I always bring the Creature with me and know how to make the most of its potential. There are times when the guilt of creating such a monster brings me back to reality, and in those rare moments, I try to do a good deed to atone for my sins.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.doctor-v-frankenstein"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"TmOHneKvHcGPqkzO","name":"Doctor V Frankenstein - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01o5f049013f95ie","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.doctor-v-frankenstein","ownerKey":"cazador.doctor-v-frankenstein","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Dark Ego Descriptor","descriptorRole":"dark-ego-descriptor","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"My mad experiments have expanded my knowledge of death and \nthe occult. I can tell the difference between science and magic. I \ngreedily desire anything I deem useful for my research and have no \nqualms about obtaining it.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"My mad experiments have expanded my knowledge of death and the occult. I can tell the difference between science and magic. I greedily desire anything I deem useful for my research and have no qualms about obtaining it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Doctor V. Frankenstein","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.doctor-v-frankenstein"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241657,"modifiedTime":1783973241657,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"j4Qq0zmVTphScIDK","name":"Captain William of Nottingham - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01h0081201iv5z1f","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Captain William of Nottingham","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.captain-william-of-nottingham","ownerKey":"cazador.captain-william-of-nottingham","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a good planner and carry all kinds of useful equipment for \nmy work. I hate sudden changes of plans.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a good planner and carry all kinds of useful equipment for my work. I hate sudden changes of plans.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Captain William of Nottingham","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.captain-william-of-nottingham"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"LiO5Fnxpq1aCzuL7","name":"Captain William of Nottingham - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01h0081201iv5z1f","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Captain William of Nottingham","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.captain-william-of-nottingham","ownerKey":"cazador.captain-william-of-nottingham","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I am a lawman and I am proud of my office. I have good \nleadership skills and know how to get those in charge to carry out \nan order. I like to be praised for my abilities.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a lawman and I am proud of my office. I have good leadership skills and know how to get those in charge to carry out an order. I like to be praised for my abilities.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Captain William of Nottingham","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.captain-william-of-nottingham"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"TStf9yBvxAYnlsY8","name":"Captain William of Nottingham - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01h0081201iv5z1f","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Captain William of Nottingham","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.captain-william-of-nottingham","ownerKey":"cazador.captain-william-of-nottingham","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"Years of working as a bounty hunter have made me adept at \nhunting down and eliminating villains. When I am one step away \nfrom my goal, I do not consider retreating.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 22.","positive":"Years of working as a bounty hunter have made me adept at hunting down and eliminating villains. When I am one step away from my goal, I do not consider retreating.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Captain William of Nottingham","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.captain-william-of-nottingham"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Z4jOeoIwo14c5FOI","name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00ns94tw01xjc1sb","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae","ownerKey":"cazador.pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I am a rebel who is used to living on the streets. I know my way \naround the slums and how to deal with the lowlifes. Rules are \nmade to be broken.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a rebel who is used to living on the streets. I know my way around the slums and how to deal with the lowlifes. Rules are made to be broken.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"I5BL6gQwKNgHakLi","name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00ns94tw01xjc1sb","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae","ownerKey":"cazador.pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I fear nothing and throw myself into any situation. The \nadrenaline of risk drives me to succeed. I get bored easily in \nsituations where there is no danger.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I fear nothing and throw myself into any situation. The adrenaline of risk drives me to succeed. I get bored easily in situations where there is no danger.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"FCh9rrchtm457Cyi","name":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"00ns94tw01xjc1sb","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae","ownerKey":"cazador.pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"The Cauldron Fae is always with me, in the form of a small \nfloating light. Her magic is still powerful, and I often summon \nher to wreak havoc or play tricks on humans.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 8.","positive":"The Cauldron Fae is always with me, in the form of a small floating light. Her magic is still powerful, and I often summon her to wreak havoc or play tricks on humans.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Pietrik and the Cauldron Fae","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.pietrik-and-the-cauldron-fae"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"rx8zjaptROfZB033","name":"Circe the Alchemist - Main Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01evw9sn00ul0u3m","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Circe the Alchemist","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.circe-the-alchemist","ownerKey":"cazador.circe-the-alchemist","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Descriptor 1","descriptorRole":"principal-descriptor","key":"descriptor-principal.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"Eurylochus cannot use more than one Pharmaka special effect per Scene.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Eurylochus cannot use more than one Pharmaka special effect per Scene.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Circe the Alchemist","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.circe-the-alchemist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241654,"modifiedTime":1783973241654,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pCUlqXRwbYCxIMrF","name":"Circe the Alchemist - Gift 1 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01evw9sn00ul0u3m","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Circe the Alchemist","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.circe-the-alchemist","ownerKey":"cazador.circe-the-alchemist","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"originalName":"Descriptor 2","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"I have studied alchemy with the greatest masters, and my potions can produce wondrous effects. I am so drawn to knowledge that I neglect \nmy own safety.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have studied alchemy with the greatest masters, and my potions can produce wondrous effects. I am so drawn to knowledge that I neglect my own safety.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Circe the Alchemist","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.circe-the-alchemist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"xV4DpZ5gThpseyne","name":"Circe the Alchemist - Gift 2 Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01evw9sn00ul0u3m","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Circe the Alchemist","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.circe-the-alchemist","ownerKey":"cazador.circe-the-alchemist","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"originalName":"Descriptor 3","descriptorRole":"gift-descriptor"}},"system":{"description":"Eurylochus is my faithful servant pig and helps me with every task. He \nhas an almost human intelligence and one look is enough to understand \nus. I love him like a brother.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Eurylochus is my faithful servant pig and helps me with every task. He has an almost human intelligence and one look is enough to understand us. I love him like a brother.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Circe the Alchemist","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.circe-the-alchemist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"lgrT0RheV90dtbC9","name":"Circe the Alchemist - Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":"01evw9sn00ul0u3m","flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Circe the Alchemist","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.circe-the-alchemist","ownerKey":"cazador.circe-the-alchemist","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"originalName":"Dark Ego Descriptor","descriptorRole":"dark-ego-descriptor","key":"descriptor-darkego.cazador"}},"system":{"description":"I have a special power over people who are hopelessly attracted to my \npresence. I am shy and often break down when I receive too much \nexplicit attention.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have a special power over people who are hopelessly attracted to my presence. I am shy and often break down when I receive too much explicit attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Circe the Alchemist","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.circe-the-alchemist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241655,"modifiedTime":1783973241655,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
